{
  "stem": "18581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 392.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They simply started to take us in groups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our group was taken via Czechoslovakia, Hungary, to Romania, in the hope that-- to set sail from one of the Black Sea ports.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened was that the Russians prevented any ships from leaving.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they decided that we'll try Italy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they brought us from Romania via Austria from the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Russian part into the British part, under very clever tricks--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--that the Jewish Brigade group--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put us in huge trucks of the Jewish Brigade group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when-- they had false papers and-- that send them there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody saw us inside the trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the British military police stops stopped them and asked them, what-- what is their mission, they said, this is a very secret mission.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's TTG.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the British asked, what is TTG?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They say, [NON-ENGLISH], which means, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "TGB is in Arabic the same thing, Geschaften means business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the-- the British didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we-- we crossed through in Tarvisio.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to Mestre in Venice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we felt really free for the first time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember we went to Mestre to the entertainment park.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we rant those little motor cars, you know, electric cars that collide with one another, like children, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after that we were in Italy until the Berihah told us one day to go again using the British army Palestine units, Jewish units, trucks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went to Monopoli in southern Italy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we left for Palestine, which we reached before Rosh Hashanah, I believe.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
